 Chgfmt [M:BIC3]PCCCOD With "K:40X"           # Issue X3-149911 - 2019-07-31 by UB : Enabling Cost type column
 Call PJT_MODFCY([M:BIC0]FCY, "[M:BIC3]PJTLIN") From TRTPJT
